dict.string: MULTI SELECT: Add item to clipboard
lpass show --sync=no --clip --${copy_field} "${item_id}" && echo "${copy_field} copied to clipboard" || echo "Error copying ${copy_field} clipboard!"
lpass ls --sync=now 1> /dev/null && echo "Sync completed" || echo "Sync error!"
lpass logout -f 1> /dev/null && echo "Logged out" || echo "Error logging out!"
lpass rm --sync=now "${item_id}" && echo "${item_name} deleted!" || echo "Error deleting ${item_name}"
Run manual sync of Lastpass vault
A comma-separated list of your private folders. Used for searching in only private entries.
When enabled, the workflow will send a notification on an action. E.g. login, sync, copy to clipboard.
